org.apache.plc4x.java.isotp.netty.model.types

Enum ParameterCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ParameterCode>
      • org.apache.plc4x.java.isotp.netty.model.types.ParameterCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ParameterCode>

    public enum ParameterCode
extends Enum<ParameterCode>
    Generally based upon RFC 905, but there were some inconsistencies in the spec: - RESIDUAL_ERROR_RATE was defined twice with different codes - The code 0x89 was defined for two types. This version was extracted from information generated by the PcapGenerator.
